phases/lifecycle
----------------
clean
init # create directories, etc
validate
process-resources
compile
compile-test
test
integration-test
jar
package?
verify # check code coverage, or whatev

scopes
------
all # similar to maven and ivy compile, this is the default
test 
compile # compilation only
provided # available for compilation only, provided by container, non-transitive
runtime # not necessary for compile

